    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126600_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126600/208_126600_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "A Goop that always makes me smile Is this one: Marmaduke Argyll. His mouth is full from cheek to cheek, Why should he then attempt to speak? It makes me smile, but still, the fact is, It is a most unpleasant practice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126600_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126600/208_126600_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "Freddie Fisher fairly fussed When he came to eat his crust! Often on the floor he'd throw it, Hoping mother wouldn't know it! Goops all hate to eat the crust; If you're told to, then you must!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126600_000058_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126600/208_126600_000058_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "How thoughtless was Roberto Lees! (For only thoughtless children tease). He teased the little pussy cat, He teased the puppy! Think of that! He even teased his sister, too! I think he was a Goop-don't you?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126600_000070_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126600/208_126600_000070_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "Young Alexander b McGiff Each day had a clean handkerchief. In spite of this, if you'll believe, He wiped his nose upon his sleeve! Nobody but a Goop would do it; His mother'd scold him, if she knew it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126600_000088_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126600/208_126600_000088_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "\"I won't!\" says young Amelia Pratt; \"I won't do this!\" \"I won't do that!\" Now isn't \"won't\" the naughtiest word That anyone has ever heard? Now isn't that the rudest way A Goop could answer? I should say!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126600_000100_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126600/208_126600_000100_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "Just look at Percival b Sloop, A most unpleasant sort of Goop; He pokes his fingers in his nose And wipes his hands upon his clothes; He does a lot of things that you, I know, would never, never do!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "And often even after they got well, they did not want to go away-they liked the Doctor and his house so much.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "So in this way he went on getting more and more pets.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "So he took the monkey away from the Italian, gave the man a shilling and told him to go.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "He asked couldn't he sleep in the fish pond at the bottom of the garden, if he promised not to eat the fish.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000007_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000007_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "But to every one in the house he was always as gentle as a kitten.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "But he wept such big tears, and begged so hard to be allowed to stay, that the Doctor hadn't the heart to turn him out.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "This is the last straw.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "\"I don't care what you call it,\" said his sister.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "\"It's a nasty thing to find under the bed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "\"But he has promised me,\" the Doctor answered, \"that he will not bite any one.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "Don't be so fussy.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "With all these mouths to fill, and the house to look after, and no one to do the mending, and no money coming in to pay the butcher's bill, things began to look very difficult.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "At least we can do that much.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "So it was agreed that the monkey, Chee Chee, was to do the cooking and mending; the dog was to sweep the floors; the duck was to dust and make the beds; the owl, Too Too, was to keep the accounts, and the pig was to do the gardening.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-208_126851_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/208/126851/208_126851_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-208",
        "content": "But still they didn't seem to make enough money to pay all the bills-and still the Doctor wouldn't worry.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
